sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Operator
    participant UI as /app/onboarding
    participant SF as ServerFn (auth)
    participant DB as Supabase (RLS)
    participant V as Vault (AES-GCM)
    participant G as Google OAuth
    participant WP as WordPress REST

    U->>UI: Step 1 — tenant details
    UI->>SF: tenants.createTenant({name, geo, vertical})
    SF->>DB: insert tenants + memberships(owner) + onboarding_sessions
    DB-->>SF: tenant_id
    SF-->>UI: ok

    U->>UI: Step 2 — WordPress URL
    UI->>SF: siteConnections.startWpConnect
    SF-->>UI: instructions + connection_id

    U->>WP: create application password
    U->>UI: paste username + app password
    UI->>SF: verifyWpConnect
    SF->>WP: GET /wp-json/wp/v2/users/me (basic auth)
    WP-->>SF: 200 user
    SF->>V: encrypt(appPassword)
    SF->>DB: tenant_secrets + site_connections(status=connected)

    U->>UI: Step 3 — Connect GSC
    UI->>SF: startOAuth(gsc)
    SF-->>UI: redirect URL
    U->>G: consent
    G->>SF: /api/public/oauth/google/callback?code&state
    SF->>G: exchange code
    SF->>V: encrypt(refresh_token)
    SF->>DB: site_connections(gsc, connected)

    Note over UI: Step 4 identical for GA4

    UI->>SF: onboarding.complete
    SF->>DB: onboarding_sessions.status = 'connected'
    SF-->>UI: redirect /app
